  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'If you are reading this I have likely been gone for a long time. Locking
    you away in here is a cruetly, but it is a greater cruetly for you to experience
    the rot and decay our world has become.

    I know you can''t stay there forever
    though, even if I am unable to be there. At the bottom of our home is the key
    to unlock the front door, though to get there you need to past some tests I have
    set up for you.

    If you get through them all then I beg you to run as far
    as you can away from here. Do not try to follow my own path, for I fear you will
    share whatever fate I get.'
